scalability, flexibility, and improved disaster recovery capabilities. However, there are still knowledge
gaps in the field, particularly regarding cybersecurity risk management in SMEs. Future research should
focus on addressing these gaps and further exploring the factors influencing cloud computing adoption
and cybersecurity practices among MSMEs.
